<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>والدارقطني <span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> والخطيب في <span class="c1">"التاريخ"</span> <span class="c2">(٩/ ٣٤٦)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
