<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>و <span class="c2">(٤٣)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>عن روح بن القاسم البصري<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وابن أبي شيبة <span class="c2">(١/ ١٦٨ - ١٦٩ و ٣٣١)</span> وابن ماجه <span class="c2">(٢٨٧ و ٦٩١)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
